						<summary>

						

						<p>This inscription registers the gift of two garlands every day to be offered to the deity Ādivarāhasvāmin and Ambujavaḷḷi-Nāñchāramma by a maid of honour who is attached to the harem of KoṇḍamanāyaniKrishanappa Nāyaka.</p>						

